- Use a vertical dropdown with `bg-white`, `shadow-md`, and `rounded-md`.
- Action items should use `text-sm text-gray-700` with `hover:bg-muted` and `cursor-pointer`.
- Include icons using `lucide-react`, aligned with `flex items-center gap-2`.
- Ensure accessibility via `role="menuitem"` and `tabIndex={0}`.
- Animate open/close with `transition-opacity duration-200 ease-in-out`.
